<section>
	<h2>Purpose</h2>
	<p>Provides the ability to split a form into steps (without/with generic validation).</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Example</h2>
	<p><progress id="updateTest" value="0" max="100">0%</progress></p>
	<div class="wb-frmvld provisional wb-steps">
		<form action="#" method="get" id="steps-example">
			<fieldset id="role" class="gc-chckbxrdio">
				<legend>What is you role?</legend>
				<p>My Relationship to the Deceased is:</p>
				<div class="radio">
					<label for="nok-1"><input type="radio" name="ethics1" value="defNot-1" id="defNot-1"/>&#160;Next of kin</label>&#160;
					<label for="fiend-1"><input type="radio" name="ethics1" value="probNot-1" id="probNot-1"/>&#160;A friend</label>&#160;
					<label for="rep-1"><input type="radio" name="ethics1" value="maybe-1" id="maybe-1"/>&#160;Legal rep</label>&#160;
					<label for="exec-1"><input type="radio" name="ethics1" value="probably-1" id="probably-1"/>&#160;Executor</label>&#160;
				</div>
			</fieldset>
			<fieldset id="age" class="gc-chckbxrdio">
				<legend>Age of the deceased?</legend>
				<p>How old was the deceased person at the time of death?</p>
				<div class="radio">
					<label for="017-1"><input type="radio" name="ethics1" value="defNot-1" id="defNot-1"/>&#160;0-17</label>&#160;
					<label for="1859-1"><input type="radio" name="ethics1" value="probNot-1" id="probNot-1"/>&#160;18-59</label>&#160;
					<label for="60-1"><input type="radio" name="ethics1" value="maybe-1" id="maybe-1"/>&#160;60+</label>&#160;
				</div>
			</fieldset class="gc-chckbxrdio">
			<fieldset id="location">
				<legend>Location of the Deceased?</legend>
				<p>Did the death occur in Canada or outside Canada?</p>
				<div class="radio">
					<label for="incanada-1"><input type="radio" name="ethics1" value="defNot-1" id="defNot-1"/>&#160;Inside Canada</label>&#160;
					<label for="outcanada-1"><input type="radio" name="ethics1" value="probNot-1" id="probNot-1"/>&#160;Outside Canada</label>&#160;
				</div>
			</fieldset>
			<fieldset id="location">
				<legend>Location of the Deceased?</legend>
				<p>Did the death occur in Canada or outside Canada?</p>
				<div class="radio">
					<label for="incanada-1"><input type="checkbox" name="ethics1" value="defNot-1" id="defNot-1"/>&#160;Inside Canada</label>&#160;
					<label for="outcanada-1"><input type="checkbox" name="ethics1" value="probNot-1" id="probNot-1"/>&#160;Outside Canada</label>&#160;
					<label for="incanada-1"><input type="checkbox" name="ethics1" value="defNot-1" id="defNot-1"/>&#160;Inside Canada</label>&#160;
					<label for="outcanada-1"><input type="checkbox" name="ethics1" value="probNot-1" id="probNot-1"/>&#160;Outside Canada</label>&#160;
					<label for="incanada-1"><input type="checkbox" name="ethics1" value="defNot-1" id="defNot-1"/>&#160;Inside Canada</label>&#160;
					<label for="outcanada-1"><input type="checkbox" name="ethics1" value="probNot-1" id="probNot-1"/>&#160;Outside Canada</label>&#160;
					<label for="incanada-1"><input type="checkbox" name="ethics1" value="defNot-1" id="defNot-1"/>&#160;Inside Canada</label>&#160;
					<label for="outcanada-1"><input type="checkbox" name="ethics1" value="probNot-1" id="probNot-1"/>&#160;Outside Canada</label>&#160;
				</div>
			</fieldset>
			<input type="submit" name="submit" value="Submit" class="btn btn-primary" />
		</form>
	</div>

	<details class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md">
		<summary>View code</summary>
		<ol>
			<li>Create a <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> element with class <code>wb-steps</code> (you can also add class <code>wb-frmvld</code> for validation).
				<pre><code>&lt;div class=&quot;wb-frmvld wb-steps&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
			</li>
			<li>Within previous the <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> element add a <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> element.
				<pre><code>&lt;form action="#" method="get" id="steps-example"&gt;&lt;/form&gt;</code></pre>
			</li>
			<li>Within previous the <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> element add your <code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> element which will need an <code>&lt;legend&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>.
				<small>These will become your steps</small>
				<pre><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;<br/>&lt;legend&gt;Client Information&lt;/legend&gt;<br/>&lt;div&gt;(Any content in the div will be hidden.)&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;/fieldset&gt;</code></pre>
			</li>
		</ol>
	</details>

	<noscript>
		<p>Steps form cannot be used without JavaScript. Instead the form will convert back to an normal form and will rely on browser/server validation (not part of WET).</p>
	</noscript>
</section>
